name: Gold Filled Custom Initial Necklace
description:
Delicate-tiny 14K gold filled oval initial charm-suspended from a sparkling 16" gold filled cable chain. Also available in sterling silver. All Adorned Article Jewelry comes beautifully wrapped and ready for gift giving. Please indicate what initial you would like on your necklace in message to seller section at checkout.

Expedited Next Day Shipping is also available.
* In an effort to save packaging materials and keep shipping costs down-unless otherwise requested mulitple pieces will be wrapped together. If you purchase multiple items and wish to have them wrapped seperately an additional charge for packaging and shipping will apply. Please contact me at time of purchase to make arrangements.
